We have consulted these resources to craft the Meowist interpretation of the Meow Meh Jing, aka The Book of Meow.

1 Stephen Mitchell. Tao Te Ching, pocket edition. HarperCollins, 1988.
2 Hua-Ching Ni. The Complete Works of Lao Tzu: Tao Teh Ching & Hua Hu Ching. Los Angeles: Seven Star Communications, 1979, 1995.
3 Ursula K Le Guin. Lao Tzu Tao Te Ching: A Book About The Way and The Power of The Way. Boston: Shambhala, 1997.
4 Bennett B Sims. Lao-Tzu and The Tao Te Ching: Immortals of Philosophy and Religion. New York: Franklin Watts Inc, 1971.
